% Plain language summary:
% Climate change is shifting the timing of leafout in forests, but given the complexity of environmental cues that determine leafout timing, we do not understand what drives differences across sites and species. We found similar leafout across temperate forests, but with a surprising amount of unexplained variation, suggesting there are gaps in our understanding of this important life history event. 

